answer: The tag tiddler must already exist and have a `list` field containing the tiddlers you want to reorder for `list-links-draggable` to work; a tag pill can find tagged tiddlers regardless of whether the tag tiddler exists, and a drag-to-reorder will automatically create the `list` field if needed.
